    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK125">
<l>ellārkku naṉṟām paṇita lavaruḷḷuñ</l>
<l>celvarkkē celvan takaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Humility is good in everyone—but among them,</l>
<l>it is in the great the greatest fortune.</l>
            </lg>
